"tid":2463041,"uid":163945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"辰 同未土係咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"地支囉，一個陽一個陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統派就認為辰土係濕土係庫，但我哋都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d6e9752a7d8332279d26e67e0cf58b7d08ca1d","tid":2463041,"uid":163945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f0debb6c278f78089423e2c42ef12f1aa63d24f","tid":2463041,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95848ce5bdbed3307369d29f226820a156d1cc01","tid":2463041,"uid":163945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"辰 同未土係咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"地支囉，一個陽一個陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統派就認為辰土係濕土係庫，但我哋都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果缺 係要點補？ 衣著 首飾？"},{"pid":"574f6467b80b7369ed6326798239c9b70f591da8","tid":2463041,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87d6e9752a7d8332279d26e67e0cf58b7d08ca1d","tid":2463041,"uid":163945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f0debb6c278f78089423e2c42ef12f1aa63d24f","tid":2463041,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95848ce5bdbed3307369d29f226820a156d1cc01","tid":2463041,"uid":163945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"辰 同未土係咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"地支囉，一個陽一個陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統派就認為辰土係濕土係庫，但我哋都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果缺 係要點補？ 衣著 首飾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"補法上冇分別，都係用衣食住行嘅五行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實八字可以十神、五行並用<br />\n<br />\n唔理你用傳統派定五行派，捉到用神就可以咁用<br />\n<br />\n本窮狗係庚金日主，假設我用神係火，而火係庚金嘅官殺星<br />\n<br />\n即係話除咗生活上補火之外，仲可以「修」官星嘅性格，即係做事講規矩原則、一板一眼、對自己要求高 etc.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用埋十神幾好玩㗎"},{"pid":"9f63abf0ca9dc60802426f356a540bc893eef6b9","tid":2463041,"uid":376361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264f6be0c5c2347faab5790140d8ac132ca31832","tid":2463041,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f63abf0ca9dc60802426f356a540bc893eef6b9","tid":2463041,"uid":376361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"1. 其實有，不過都係同我哋個 theory 有關<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋唔太相信完全定命論，所以我哋係冇一個系統算到你家底點、有幾多兄弟姊妹、有幾多個仔女、一世搵幾多錢、另一半點個樣、幾時死 etc. 𠵱類宿命嘅神算問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 天干地支互不相干，甚至可以矛盾，所以地支唔可以用天干通關<br />\n<br />\n但我又用我日主（庚金）假設，如果天干遇丙火又冇印、比、食去擋，咁我即係會嗰段時間日主受剋<br />\n<br />\n但日主受剋都有分程度，我可能只係大壓力，亦有可能出意外傷亡，要更準確判斷就要睇埋地支<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我流年走申金，流月再走午火，咁地支就剋申金，而因為申金 == 庚金，所以就變咗地支版日主受剋<br />\n<br />\n𠵱個時候天干地支同時受剋，就係地獄黑仔嘅時間，比較大機會有大傷亡"},{"pid":"8fe9483846d0a1b8a8093cd260ce35d064f31a20","tid":2463041,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/llZW2dvxB5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FllZW2dvxB5c&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e4effab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/llZW2dvxB5c</a><br />\n八字斷終生？𠵱個命題講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272fc120fdb7ca6f84cad483a22cb1d03a5a2394","tid":2463041,"uid":233874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇Matlab大神"}]}